OL,5,Capproved
OL,7,Fhas approved plans to increase council
OL,8,Ftax by 21%, make #300m in cuts and
OL,9,Fscale back public services.
OL,11,FThe Labour-run council declared itself
OL,12,Feffectively bankrupt in September last
OL,13,Fyear, after identifying equal pay
OL,14,Fliabilities estimated at #760 million,
OL,15,Fand is now said to be on a "narrow
OL,16,Fpath to financial sustainability"
OL,17,Fdependent on budget cuts.
