OL,7,FThe five-hour council meeting was told
OL,8,F#300 million of cuts over two years,
OL,9,Fincluding to library services, were
OL,10,Fneeded to secure #1.255 billion in
OL,11,Fexceptional financial support (EFS)
OL,12,Floans from central Government.
OL,14,FA separate motion recommending a
OL,15,Fcouncil tax rise of 9.99% ` taking
OL,16,Fannual bills for a Band D property to
OL,17,F#1,793 ` was also approved.
