OL,7,FHe said: "It is not a budget I ever
OL,8,Fenvisaged for our city. Sadly however,
OL,9,Fit is a budget that reflects the
OL,10,Fsignificant challenges currently
OL,11,Ffacing this council.
OL,13,F"Because the harsh reality is we must
OL,14,Fmake cuts of over #300 million over
OL,15,Fthe next two financial years in order
OL,16,Fto receive exceptional financial
OL,17,Fsupport from Government and to meet
OL,18,Fthe challenge set by commissioners.
