OL,7,F"As the report before us states, that
OL,8,Fis unprecedented in scale and, for
OL,9,Fthat, I unreservedly apologise to the
OL,10,Fpeople and communities of our city.
OL,12,F"The fact remains however that my
OL,13,Ftask, as the new leader of the
OL,14,Fcouncil, is to tackle financial and
OL,15,Forganisational challenges that have
OL,16,Fdogged this organisation for far too
OL,17,Flong.
OL,19,F"Quite simply, we must get our house
OL,20,Fin order, because the people of our
OL,21,Fgreat city deserve better."
